=== CRYSTALLINE_ENTITY ===
# id: 25
# title: The Crystalline Entity
# chinese_title: 晶体生命
# category: Alien
# mode: dungeon

A being of living crystal hovers before you, its body refracting light into rainbow cascades. It communicates through pulses of color and harmonic vibrations. Your translator struggles but manages fragments: it is lost, separated from its cluster. It seems to be asking for help.

* [Help it send a signal to its cluster]
  ~ gain_radical("气")
  "气" (qì) — air, energy, spirit
* [Offer it energy from your power cells]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "帮" (bāng) — to help
* [Study its crystalline structure]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "晶" (jīng) — crystal, bright
* [Back away slowly]
  ~ nothing
  "退" (tuì) — to retreat, to back away
